data.description: This inviting 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home sits back off the road enveloped in mature shade trees on a quarter acre lot. Within you will find new luxury vinyl flooring and fresh paint throughout. For year-round comfort, this home is equipped with both central air conditioning, a heat pump and a wood stove for efficient heating. You'll enjoy a comfortable climate no matter the season. A fully fenced backyard with deck for relaxing or entertaining adds to the appeal of this turn key home. Conveniently located, this home provides easy access to schools and downtown. Schedule a viewing today to see all this home has to offer!
